  "summary": {
    "en": "A 130-piece STEM construction toy for forts, tents, glow-style structures, and parent-child play.",
    "zh": "130件STEM拼搭玩具，适合堡垒、帐篷、夜光风格结构和亲子互动。"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": [
      "The 130-piece configuration is suitable for indoor forts, tent frames, geometric towers, and imaginative STEM play.",
      "PP parts are lightweight and durable for repeated assembly at home, in classrooms, or during activity programs.",
      "Glow-themed styling increases gift appeal and supports night-play storytelling.",
      "The set is suitable for retail, education, and OEM/ODM projects with custom packaging options."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "130件配置适合室内堡垒、帐篷框架、几何高塔和创意STEM玩法。",
      "PP配件轻便耐用，适合家庭、课堂或活动项目中的反复拼装。",
      "夜光主题风格增强礼品吸引力，并支持夜间故事玩法。",
      "套装适合零售、教育和OEM/ODM项目，可沟通定制包装。"
    ]
  },
